records.name: Whiteshell Island Hotel & Spa

descriptions.direction: Located in Maafushi, WhiteShell Island Hotel & Spa is near the beach. Maldives Islamic Centre and Mulee Aage Palace are local landmarks, and some of the area's activities can be experienced at Maafushi Harbor and Bolifushi Island Pier. Take an opportunity to explore the area for water adventures such as fishing.
descriptions.general: Located on Maafushi Island in the Maldives, this small private hotel is an ideal place to get away from it all and relax on some of the world's best beaches. The accommodation is a 30-minute speed boat ride to Maafushi and the nearest international airport is at Male. Guests can enjoy diving and snorkelling in the warm seas. Catamaran trips, excursions to nearby uninhabited islands and sandbanks, and night fishing trips are available and local bodu-beru cultural shows are provided. The inviting beach-front guest accommodation consists of double deluxe and family deluxe rooms, all featuring individually controlled air conditioning and a ceiling fan. The island's restaurants are renowned for their quality and service and gourmet cuisine. The on-site White Shell café is open until 2. 00 serving delicious drinks and snacks, and beach barbecues can be arranged.
